# ===== Summary =====
#
# Files Modified:
# - Backend: 4 files (config.py, config_helper.py, redis_keys.py, manager.py)
# - Frontend: 3 files (constants.js, ProxySettingsForm.jsx, ProxySettingsFormUtils.js)
#
# Features:
# - Redis-based cooldown system (10 minutes default)
# - Last resort: clears all cooldowns when all combinations tried
# - Per default DISABLED (stream_cooldown_enabled: false)
# - UI: Checkbox + NumberInput (0-1440 minutes = 0-24 hours)
# - Prevents endless loops via tried_combinations.clear()
#
# Testing:
# 1. Default (disabled): Should behave like v0.26.0 without cooldown
# 2. Enabled: Should show [COOLDOWN] logs
# 3. Last resort: Should trigger after all combinations fail twice
